OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with a
OL,6,Ffew bright or clear intervals near the
OL,7,FMoray Firth and east of the Great
OL,8,FGlen. Otherwise it will remain cloudy
OL,9,Fand breezy with outbreaks of rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,12,Fheavy at times in the west. Dry with
OL,13,Fsome bright spells across Inverness
OL,14,Fand Nairn.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRain
OL,17,Fdying out on Monday with some
OL,18,Fbrightness coming through. Dry with
OL,19,Fplenty of sunshine and rather warm on
OL,20,FTuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
